msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`參展商選單項目`\\ ：顯示子選單項目，導覽至活動參展商頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_setup/event_templates.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Community`: Display a submenu item allowing attendees to access "
