"功能會變為可用。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_setup/event_templates.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow Room Creation`: If the :guilabel:`Community` option is "
"enabled, allow visitors to create their own community rooms."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`允許建立會議室`\\ ：如果啟用了\\ :guilabel:`社群`\\ 選項，則允"
"許訪問者建立自己的社群會議室。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_setup/event_templates.rst:51
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Register Button`: Display a button taking visitors to the event-"
"specific registration page."
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`註冊按鈕`\\ ：顯示一個按鈕，將訪問者帶到活動專屬的註冊頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_setup/event_templates.rst:54
msgid ""
"Once the desired checkboxes have been ticked, select an "
