#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize.rst:6
msgid "Promote and monetize"
msgstr "推廣和獲利"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo **Events** application provides users with the ability to create, "
"sell, and manage event booth reservations."
msgstr "Odoo\\ **活動**\\ 應用程式讓使用者能夠建立、銷售及管理活動攤位預訂。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:11
msgid ""
"In order to create, sell, and manage booths for events, the *Booth "
"Management* feature must be activated."
msgstr "若要建立、銷售和管理活動攤位，必須啟用\\ *攤位管理*\\ 功能。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:14
msgid ""
"To do that, navigate to :menuselection:`Events app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. Click the :guilabel:`Booth Management` checkbox, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save` to enable the setting."
msgstr ""
"若要執行此操作，請前往\\ :menuselection:`活動應用程式 --> 配置 --> 設定`\\ 。"
"按一下\\ :guilabel:`攤位管理`\\ 勾選方格，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`儲存`\\ 以"
"啟用該設定。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:None
msgid "The Booth Management setting in the Odoo Events application."
msgstr "Odoo 活動應用程式中的攤位管理設定。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:20
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Booth Management` setting is activated, Odoo "
"automatically creates a default *Event Booth* product in the database with "
"its :guilabel:`Product Type` set to :guilabel:`Service` and "
"its :guilabel:`Create on Order` field set to :guilabel:`Event Booth`."
msgstr ""
"當\\ :guilabel:`攤位管理`\\ 設定啟用時，Odoo 會自動在資料庫中建立預設的 *活動"
"攤位* 產品，其\\ :guilabel:`產品類型`\\ 設定為\\ :guilabel:`服務`\\ ，且其\\ "
":guilabel:`訂單建立時`\\ 欄位設定為\\ :guilabel:`活動攤位`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:24
msgid ""
"Users can modify/duplicate this default product or create a new, custom "
"product. In either case, users **must** verify that an *Event Booth* product "
"exists with this configuration in order to create booths and booth "
"categories, as shown later in this documentation."
msgstr ""
"使用者可以修改／複製此預設產品或建立新的自訂產品。無論哪種情況，使用者**必"
"須**確認存在具有此配置的 *活動攤位* 產品，才能建立攤位和攤位類別，如本使用說"
"明稍後所示。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:31
msgid "Booth categories"
msgstr "攤位類別"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:33
msgid ""
"Custom *booth categories* can be created by users to assign different price "
"tiers and :doc:`sponsors <event_sponsors>` for multiple booths at once."
msgstr ""
"使用者可以建立自訂的 *攤位類別*，以便一次為多個攤位指定不同的價格層級和\\ "
":doc:`贊助商 <event_sponsors>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:36
msgid ""
"When the *Booth Management* setting is activated, Odoo automatically creates "
"three default booth categories: *Standard Booth*, *Premium Booth*, and *VIP "
"Booth*. Users can modify/duplicate these default categories or create new, "
"custom categories. In either case, booth categories **must** exist in the "
"database before users can create event booths."
msgstr ""
"當 *攤位管理* 設定啟用時，Odoo 會自動建立三個預設攤位類別：*標準攤位*、*進階"
"攤位* 和 *VIP 攤位*。使用者可以修改／複製這些預設類別或建立新的自訂類別。無論"
"哪種情況，資料庫中**必須**存在攤位類別，使用者才能建立活動攤位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:42
msgid "Booth categories dashboard"
msgstr "攤位類別 Dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:44
msgid ""
"To view and manage booth categories, navigate to :menuselection:`Events app "
"--> Configuration --> Booth Categories`."
msgstr ""
"若要檢視及管理攤位類別，請前往\\ :menuselection:`活動應用程式 --> 配置 --> 攤"
"位類別`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:47
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Booth Category` dashboard displays a list of all created "
"booth categories along with the booth category name, associated *Event "
"Booth* product, and price."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`攤位類別`\\ Dashboard 會顯示所有已建立攤位類別的清單，以及攤位類別"
"名稱、關聯的 *活動攤位* 產品和價格。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:51
msgid ""
"If sponsors are enabled in the **Events** app, an additional *Create "
"Sponsor* checkbox appears on each record in the list as well as on the booth "
"category form."
msgstr ""
"如果在\\ **活動**\\ 應用程式中啟用了贊助商，清單中的每筆記錄以及攤位類別表單"
"上都會出現額外的 *建立贊助商* 勾選方格。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:None
msgid "The Booth Category page in the Odoo Events application."
msgstr "Odoo 活動應用程式中的攤位類別頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:57
msgid ""
"To edit an existing booth category, select it from the list and proceed to "
"make any desired modifications in the resulting booth category form."
msgstr ""
"若要編輯現有攤位類別，請從清單中選取該類別，然後在產生的攤位類別表單中進行任"
"何所需的修改。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:63
msgid "Create booth category"
msgstr "建立攤位類別"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:65
msgid ""
"To create a booth category, click the :guilabel:`New` button in the upper-"
"left corner of the page to reveal a blank booth category form."
msgstr ""
"若要建立攤位類別，請按一下頁面左上角的\\ :guilabel:`新增`\\ 按鈕以顯示空白的"
"攤位類別表單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:None
msgid "A typical booth category form in the Odoo Events application."
msgstr "Odoo 活動應用程式中的典型攤位類別表單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:71
msgid ""
"Start by entering a name for the booth category in the top :guilabel:`Booth "
"Category` field. This is a **required** field."
msgstr ""
"首先在頂端的\\ :guilabel:`攤位類別`\\ 欄位中輸入攤位類別名稱。這是**必填**欄"
"位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:74
msgid ""
"Optionally, upload a corresponding image (e.g., a sample photo of how the "
"booth looks)."
msgstr "您可以選擇上傳對應的圖片（例如，攤位外觀的範例照片）。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:76
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Booth Details` section, assign an *Event Booth* product in "
"the :guilabel:`Product` field. This a **required** field."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`攤位詳細資訊`\\ 區段中，於\\ :guilabel:`產品`\\ 欄位中指定 "
"*活動攤位* 產品。這是**必填**欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:79
msgid ""
"Next, set a price for the booth category in the :guilabel:`Price` field."
msgstr "接下來，在\\ :guilabel:`價格`\\ 欄位中為攤位類別設定價格。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:81
msgid ""
"If event sponsors are configured, a :guilabel:`Sponsorship` section appears "
"with a :guilabel:`Create Sponsor` checkbox option. When enabled, the user is "
"created as an official *Sponsor* of the event whenever a booth of this "
"category is booked."
msgstr ""
"如果已配置活動贊助商，則會出現\\ :guilabel:`贊助`\\ 區段，其中包含\\ "
":guilabel:`建立贊助商`\\ 勾選方格選項。啟用後，當預訂此類別的攤位時，使用者會"
"建立為活動的正式 *贊助商*。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:85
msgid ""
"Additionally, the :guilabel:`Sponsor Level` and :guilabel:`Sponsor Type` "
"fields can be configured to specify the level/tier and the type of "
"sponsorship. See the :doc:`event sponsors <event_sponsors>` documentation "
"for more information about configuring sponsor levels and types."
msgstr ""
"此外，可以配置\\ :guilabel:`贊助商級別`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`贊助商類型`\\ 欄位"
"，以指定贊助的級別／層級和類型。有關配置贊助商級別和類型的更多資訊，請參閱\\ "
":doc:`活動贊助商 <event_sponsors>`\\ 使用說明。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:89
msgid ""
"Finally, in the :guilabel:`Description` tab, enter any information about the "
"booth category (e.g., the square footage, any amenities, size of display "
"screen, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"最後，在\\ :guilabel:`說明`\\ 分頁中，輸入關於攤位類別的任何資訊（例如，平方"
"英尺數、任何設施、顯示螢幕大小等）。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:93
msgid "Add booths to events"
msgstr "將攤位加入活動"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:95
msgid ""
"After configuring booth categories, booths can be created and added to "
"specific events."
msgstr "配置展位類別後，即可建立展位並加入特定活動。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:98
msgid "Booths dashboard"
msgstr "展位\\ Dashboard"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:100
msgid ""
"To create and add booths to a specific event, first navigate to its event "
"form and click the :guilabel:`Booths` smart button at the top to access "
"the :guilabel:`Booths` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"要建立展位並加入特定活動，請先前往其活動表單，然後按一下頂部的\\ "
":guilabel:`展位`\\ 智慧按鈕以存取\\ :guilabel:`展位` Dashboard。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:103
msgid ""
"The dashboard is displayed in a Kanban view, by default, and grouped by two "
"different: :guilabel:`Available` and :guilabel:`Unavailable`. The booths in "
"the :guilabel:`Available` stage are still available for exhibitors to "
"reserve. The booths in the :guilabel:`Unavailable` stage have already been "
"reserved and are no longer available."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard 預設以看板檢視顯示，並依兩種不同狀態分組：:guilabel:`可用`\\ 和\\ "
":guilabel:`無法使用`。:guilabel:`可用`\\ 階段中的展位仍可供參展商預約"
"。:guilabel:`無法使用`\\ 階段中的展位已被預約且不再可用。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:109
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Booths` dashboard is also viewable in a :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(List)`, :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(Graph)`, "
"or :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` views for users to track "
"insights about booths for a particular event."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`展位` Dashboard 也可用\\ :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`（清單"
"）`、:icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`（圖表）`\\ 或\\ :icon:`oi-view-pivot` "
":guilabel:`（樞紐）`\\ 檢視方式顯示，供使用者追蹤特定活動展位的深入分析。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:113
msgid ""
"In addition to the default :guilabel:`Available` and :guilabel:`Unavailable` "
"filters, the **Booths** dashboard can be grouped by the following:"
msgstr ""
"除了預設的\\ :guilabel:`可用`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`無法使用`\\ 篩選條件外，**展"
"位** Dashboard 還可依下列項目分組："

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:116
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Status`: Group by the availability of the booths. This is the "
"default grouping option."
msgstr ":guilabel:`狀態`：依展位可用性分組。這是預設分組選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:117
msgid ":guilabel:`Renter`: Group by the individual renters of the booths."
msgstr ":guilabel:`租用者`：依展位個別租用者分組。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Booth Category`: Group by the booth categories of the booths."
msgstr ":guilabel:`展位類別`：依展位的展位類別分組。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:119
msgid ":guilabel:`Is Paid`: Group by booths that have been paid and reserved."
msgstr ":guilabel:`已付款`：依已付款並預約的展位分組。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:120
msgid ":guilabel:`Event`: Group by the associated event of the booths."
msgstr ":guilabel:`活動`：依展位所屬活動分組。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:122
msgid ""
"See the :doc:`reporting <../../../essentials/reporting>` documentation for "
"more information about views and how to apply filters and grouping options."
msgstr ""
"請參閱\\ :doc:`報表 <../../../essentials/reporting>`\\ 使用說明以取得有關檢視"
"以及如何套用篩選和分組選項的更多資訊。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:127
msgid "Create an event booth"
msgstr "建立活動展位"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:129
msgid ""
"To create a new booth, click :guilabel:`New` in either the Kanban or List "
"view. This opens an event booth form for the user to configure a new booth."
msgstr ""
"要建立新展位，請在看板或清單檢視中按一下\\ :guilabel:`新增`。這會開啟活動展位"
"表單，供使用者配置新展位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:None
msgid "Typical booth form in the Odoo Events application."
msgstr "Odoo 活動應用程式中的典型攤位表單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:135
msgid ""
"Start by typing in a :guilabel:`Name` for the booth. This is a **required** "
"field."
msgstr "首先為攤位輸入\\ :guilabel:`名稱`。這是\\ **必填**\\ 欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:137
msgid ""
"Then, apply (or :ref:`create <events/booth-categories/create>`) "
"a :guilabel:`Booth Category`. This is a **required** field."
msgstr ""
"然後套用（或\\ :ref:`建立 <events/booth-categories/create>`）:guilabel:`展位"
"類別`。這是**必填**欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:140
msgid ""
"After selecting an existing :guilabel:`Booth Category`, the corresponding "
"product and price of the selected booth category appear in the non-"
"modifiable :guilabel:`Product` and :guilabel:`Price` fields."
msgstr ""
"選擇現有\\ :guilabel:`展位類別`\\ 後，所選展位類別對應的產品和價格會顯示在無"
"法修改的\\ :guilabel:`產品`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`價格`\\ 欄位中。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:144
msgid ""
"Continue by selecting a renter's contact in the :guilabel:`Renter` drop-down "
"to automatically populate the :guilabel:`Renter Name`, :guilabel:`Renter "
"Email`, and :guilabel:`Renter Phone` fields. Alternatively, these fields can "
"also be entered manually."
msgstr ""
"繼續在\\ :guilabel:`租用者`\\ 下拉式選單中選擇租用者的聯絡人，即可自動填入\\ "
":guilabel:`租用者名稱`、:guilabel:`租用者電子郵件`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`租用者電"
"話`\\ 欄位。或者，這些欄位也可手動輸入。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:149
msgid ""
"When a renter :ref:`reserves a booth <events/booth-reservation/reserving>` "
"through the event website, the renter-related fields on the form "
"automatically populate based on the information provided during the online "
"transaction. The booth then automatically changes status from *Available* to "
"*Unavailable*."
msgstr ""
"當租用者透過活動網站\\ :ref:`預約展位 <events/booth-reservation/reserving>`\\"
" 時，表單上租用者相關欄位會依據線上交易期間提供的資訊自動填入。展位狀態會自動"
"從*可用*變更為*無法使用*。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:154
msgid ""
"The status of the booth (:guilabel:`Available` or :guilabel:`Unavailable`) "
"can also be changed manually, either by clicking the appropriate status from "
"the status bar in the upper-right of the booth form or by dragging-and-"
"dropping the desired booth into the appropriate stage via the *Booths* "
"dashboard Kanban view."
msgstr ""
"展位狀態（:guilabel:`可用`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`無法使用`）也可手動變更，方法是"
"在展位表單右上角的狀態列中按一下適當狀態，或透過*展位* Dashboard 看板檢視將所"
"需展位拖放至適當階段。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:160
msgid "Event booth reservation"
msgstr "活動展位預約"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:162
msgid ""
"With event booths configured, renters can view and reserve them on the event "
"webpage via the *Get A Booth* event sub-menu link."
msgstr ""
"配置活動展位後，租用者可透過*取得展位*活動子選單連結在活動網頁上檢視並預約展"
"位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:165
msgid ""
"This section outlines how to configure the event website to allow renters to "
"reserve booths. It then provides a view of how renters can reserve the "
"booths through the website."
msgstr ""
"本節概述如何配置活動網站，以允許租戶預訂攤位。然後提供租戶如何透過網站預訂攤"
"位的檢視。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:169
msgid "Enable booth reservations"
msgstr "啟用攤位預訂"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:171
msgid ""
"To access the event booths page for a specific event, navigate to the event "
"form in the **Events** app and click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart "
"button to open the event page."
msgstr ""
"若要存取特定活動的活動攤位頁面，請在\\ **活動**\\ 應用程式中前往活動表單，然"
"後按一下\\ :guilabel:`前往網站`\\ 智慧按鈕以開啟活動頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:174
msgid ""
"If the event sub-menu (with the :guilabel:`Get A Booth` option) is *not* "
"showing up, there are two ways to make it appear: via the website edit mode "
"or through the developer mode."
msgstr ""
"如果活動子選單（包含\\ :guilabel:`取得攤位`\\ 選項）*未*顯示，有兩種方法可以"
"使其出現：透過網站編輯模式或透過開發人員模式。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:178
msgid "Website edit mode"
msgstr "網站編輯模式"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:180
msgid ""
"While on the event page, enter the edit mode by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Edit` button in the upper-right corner. Then, click into "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab of the resulting sidebar of web design tools."
msgstr ""
"在活動頁面上時，按一下右上角的\\ :guilabel:`編輯`\\ 按鈕以進入編輯模式。然後"
"，在產生的網頁設計工具側邊欄中按一下\\ :guilabel:`自訂`\\ 分頁。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:184
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, click the toggle switch for :guilabel:`Sub-"
"menu (Specific)`, then click :guilabel:`Save`. Doing so reveals the event "
"sub-menu with various options (e.g., Talks, Agenda, Info, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`自訂`\\ 分頁中，按一下\\ :guilabel:`子選單（特定）`\\ 的切換"
"開關，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`儲存`。這樣做會顯示包含各種選項（例如演講、議程"
"、資訊等）的活動子選單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:189
msgid "Developer mode"
msgstr "開發人員模式"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:191
msgid ""
"Alternatively, enter :doc:`Debug mode <../../../general/developer_mode>` and "
"open the specific event form in the **Events** application."
msgstr ""
"或者，進入\\ :doc:`偵錯模式 <../../../general/developer_mode>`\\ 並在\\ **活"
"動**應用程式中開啟特定活動表單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:194
msgid ""
"With *Debug mode* on, an array of sub-menu options appears at the top of the "
"event form. Click the checkbox for :guilabel:`Website Submenu` to display "
"the event sub-menu on the event page."
msgstr ""
"開啟*偵錯模式*後，活動表單頂部會出現一系列子選單選項。勾選\\ :guilabel:`網站"
"子選單`\\ 的勾選方格，以在活動頁面上顯示活動子選單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:197
msgid ""
"Next, choose which sub-menu options to include on the event page. In this "
"case, make sure the :guilabel:`Booth Register` checkbox is selected."
msgstr ""
"接下來，選擇要在活動頁面上包含哪些子選單選項。在這種情況下，請確保已選取\\ "
":guilabel:`攤位註冊`\\ 勾選方格。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:203
msgid "Reserve a booth"
msgstr "預訂攤位"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:205
msgid ""
"Once the sub-menu is enabled on the event page either through the website "
"editor or through the debug mode, renters can then view and reserve "
"available booths."
msgstr ""
"在透過網站編輯器或透過偵錯模式在活動頁面上啟用子選單後，租戶便可以檢視和預訂"
"可用攤位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:208
msgid ""
"Renters can access the *Get A Booth* page on the event website by selecting "
"the desired event from the :guilabel:`Events` homepage then clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Get A Booth` sub-menu option."
msgstr ""
"租戶可以從\\ :guilabel:`活動`\\ 首頁選擇所需的活動，然後按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`取得攤位`\\ 子選單選項，以存取活動網站上的*取得攤位*頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:None
msgid "Get A Booth page on the website in Odoo Events."
msgstr "Odoo 活動中網站上的「取得攤位」頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:214
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Get A Booth` page, the renter can select their desired "
"booth option, then :guilabel:`Location`. Next, they click "
"the :guilabel:`Book my Booth(s)` button located at the bottom-right of the "
"page."
msgstr ""
"從\\ :guilabel:`取得攤位`\\ 頁面，租戶可以選擇所需的攤位選項，然後選擇\\ "
":guilabel:`位置`。接下來，他們按一下位於頁面右下角的\\ :guilabel:`預訂我的攤"
"位`\\ 按鈕。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:218
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Contact Details` page where they fill out "
"either *Contact Details* or *Sponsor Details* depending on how the booth was "
"configured."
msgstr ""
"這樣做會顯示\\ :guilabel:`聯絡人詳細資料`\\ 頁面，他們可以在其中填寫*聯絡人詳"
"細資料*或*贊助商詳細資料*，具體取決於攤位的配置方式。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:221
msgid ""
"Once the necessary information has been entered, the renter then clicks "
"the :guilabel:`Go to Payment` at the bottom of the page and proceeds to "
"complete the typical :doc:`checkout process <../../../websites/ecommerce/"
"checkout>`."
msgstr ""
"輸入必要資訊後，租用者按一下頁面底部的\\ :guilabel:`前往付款`\\ ，然後繼續完"
"成典型的\\ :doc:`結帳流程 <../../../websites/ecommerce/checkout>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:225
msgid ""
"Upon a successful payment confirmation, the renter has successfully reserved "
"a booth."
msgstr "成功確認付款後，租戶即成功預訂攤位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:227
msgid ""
"In the database, that selected booth automatically moves to the "
"*Unavailable* stage on the event-specific *Booths* page in the **Events** "
"app."
msgstr ""
"在資料庫中，該選定的攤位會自動移至\\ **活動**\\ 應用程式中特定活動的*攤位*頁"
"面上的*無法使用*階段。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:230
msgid ""
"The provided *Sponsor* information (if applicable) and *Sales Order* "
"information are also accessible from the specific event form via their "
"respective smart buttons that appear at the top of the form."
msgstr ""
"提供的*贊助商*資訊（如果適用）和*銷售單*資訊也可以透過表單頂部出現的各自智慧"
"按鈕從特定活動表單存取。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_booths.rst:235
msgid ":doc:`sell_tickets`"
msgstr ":doc:`sell_tickets`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:3
msgid "Event sponsors"
msgstr "活動贊助商"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:5
msgid ""
"In the **Events** app, users can add sponsors for the event and feature them "
"online or in person as exhibitors."
msgstr ""
"在\\ **活動**\\ 應用程式中，使用者可以為活動加入贊助商，並在線上或現場將其展"
"示為參展商。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:11
msgid ""
"To allow users to create and manage event sponsors, the **Events** app must "
"first be configured by navigating to :menuselection:`Events app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"若要允許使用者建立和管理活動贊助商，必須先前往\\ :menuselection:`活動應用程"
"式 --> 配置 --> 設定`\\ 配置\\ **活動**\\ 應用程式。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:14
msgid ""
"Next, click on the :guilabel:`Online Exhibitors` checkbox. This setting "
"enables the user to create and manage event sponsors. Finally, remember to "
"click the :guilabel:`Save` button on the top-left to enable and load the "
"setting."
msgstr ""
"接著，勾選\\ :guilabel:`線上參展商`\\ 勾選方塊。此設定可讓使用者建立和管理活"
"動贊助商。最後，請記得按一下左上角的\\ :guilabel:`儲存`\\ 按鈕以啟用並載入該"
"設定。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:19
msgid "View or manage sponsors"
msgstr "檢視或管理贊助商"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:21
msgid ""
"To view and manage sponsors for an event, navigate to :menuselection:`Events "
"app --> Events` then click the relevant event."
msgstr ""
"若要檢視和管理活動的贊助商，請前往\\ :menuselection:`活動應用程式 --> 活動`\\"
" ，然後按一下相關活動。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:24
msgid ""
"At the top of the event form, click on the :icon:`fa-black-"
"tie` :guilabel:`Sponsors` smart button. This opens a list of existing "
"sponsors/exhibitors in the :icon:`oi-view-kanban` (:guilabel:`Kanban`) view. "
"Optionally, to view the sponsors in a list, click the :icon:`oi-view-list` "
"(:guilabel:`List`) view."
msgstr ""
"在活動表單頂端，按一下\\ :icon:`fa-black-tie`\\ :guilabel:`贊助商`\\ 智慧按鈕"
"。這會在\\ :icon:`oi-view-kanban`\\ （\\ :guilabel:`看板`\\ ）檢視中開啟現有"
"贊助商／參展商清單。或者，若要以清單形式檢視贊助商，請按一下\\ :icon:`oi-"
"view-list`\\ （\\ :guilabel:`清單`\\ ）檢視。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:None
msgid "Event sponsors dashboard in Odoo Events."
msgstr "Odoo 活動中的活動贊助商 Dashboard。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:32
msgid ""
"Any newly added sponsors appear on this page as cards with the sponsor logo, "
"name, type of sponsor, and contact information. Additionally, a "
"green :guilabel:`Published` banner appears in the corner when the sponsor is "
"published on the webpage."
msgstr ""
"任何新加入的贊助商都會以卡片形式顯示在此頁面上，包含贊助商標誌、名稱、贊助商"
"類型及聯絡資訊。此外，當贊助商在網頁上發佈時，角落會顯示綠色的\\ "
":guilabel:`已發佈`\\ 橫幅。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:36
msgid ""
"To delete a sponsor, click on the sponsor card. Next to the sponsor name at "
"the top-left, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon and "
"select :guilabel:`Delete`."
msgstr ""
"若要刪除贊助商，請按一下贊助商卡片。在左上角的贊助商名稱旁邊，按一下\\ "
":icon:`fa-cog`\\ :guilabel:`（齒輪）`\\ 圖示，然後選擇\\ :guilabel:`刪除`。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:40
msgid "Create a new sponsor"
msgstr "建立新贊助商"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:42
msgid ""
"On the sponsor dashboard page, click the :guilabel:`New` button at the top-"
"left to open a new event sponsor form."
msgstr ""
"在贊助商 Dashboard 頁面上，按一下左上角的\\ :guilabel:`新增`\\ 按鈕以開啟新的"
"活動贊助商表單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:None
msgid "Event sponsor form in Odoo Events."
msgstr "Odoo 活動中的活動贊助商表單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:48
msgid ""
"On the form are multiple fields to configure the sponsor's contact details "
"and type of sponsorship:"
msgstr "表單上有多個欄位可供配置贊助商的聯絡詳細資料及贊助類型："

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:50
msgid ":guilabel:`Sponsor Name`: Name of the sponsor displayed on the website."
msgstr ":guilabel:`贊助商名稱`：網站上顯示的贊助商名稱。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:51
msgid ":guilabel:`Slogan`: Slogan of the sponsor."
msgstr ":guilabel:`標語`：贊助商的標語。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Partner`: Contact of the sponsorship partner. This field is "
"**required**."
msgstr ":guilabel:`合作夥伴`：贊助合作夥伴的聯絡人。此欄位為**必填**。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:53
msgid ":guilabel:`Email`: Email of the sponsor."
msgstr ":guilabel:`電子郵件`：贊助商的電子郵件。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:54
msgid ":guilabel:`Phone`: Phone number of the sponsor."
msgstr ":guilabel:`電話`：贊助商的電話號碼。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:55
msgid ":guilabel:`Website`: Link to the sponsor's website."
msgstr ":guilabel:`網站`：贊助商網站的連結。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:56
msgid ":guilabel:`Event`: Specific event to be sponsored."
msgstr ":guilabel:`活動`：要贊助的特定活動。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:57
msgid ":guilabel:`Sponsorship Level`: Tier or level of sponsorship."
msgstr ":guilabel:`贊助等級`：贊助的層級或等級。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sponsor Type`: Type of participation of the sponsor during the "
"event."
msgstr ":guilabel:`贊助商類型`：贊助商在活動期間的參與類型。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Show on ticket`: Option to display sponsor logos on attendees' "
"registration tickets."
msgstr ":guilabel:`在票券上顯示`\\ ：在參加者的報名票券上顯示贊助商標誌的選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:61
msgid ""
"Additional fields may appear depending on the :ref:`sponsorship details "
"<event_sponsors/sponsorship-details>` provided by the user."
msgstr ""
"根據使用者提供的\\ :ref:`贊助詳情 <event_sponsors/sponsorship-details>`\\ ，"
"可能會出現其他欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:65
msgid "Contact details"
msgstr "聯絡人詳情"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:67
msgid ""
"To start, enter a name for the sponsor under the :guilabel:`Sponsor Name` "
"field."
msgstr "首先，在\\ :guilabel:`贊助商名稱`\\ 欄位下方輸入贊助商的名稱。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:69
msgid ""
"Optionally, enter the :guilabel:`Slogan`. This slogan is displayed on the "
"sponsor's page on the website."
msgstr "可選擇性輸入\\ :guilabel:`標語`。此標語會顯示在網站的贊助商頁面上。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:72
msgid ""
"Next, select or create a :guilabel:`Partner` for the sponsorship by "
"selecting a contact from the drop-down."
msgstr "接下來，從下拉式選單中選擇聯絡人，以選擇或建立贊助的\\ :guilabel:`合作夥伴`。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:75
msgid ""
"Selecting an existing partner contact will auto-populate the "
"remaining :guilabel:`Email`, :guilabel:`Phone`, :guilabel:`Mobile`, "
"and :guilabel:`Website` fields **only if** those fields are already "
"configured on the partner's contact form."
msgstr ""
"選擇現有的合作夥伴聯絡人後，只有在該合作夥伴的聯絡人表單中已配置這些欄位的情"
"況下，才會自動填入其餘的\\ :guilabel:`Email`、:guilabel:`電"
"話`、:guilabel:`Mobile`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`網站`\\ 欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:80
msgid ""
"To view this contact form, click the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(right)` arrow at the right of the :guilabel:`Partner` "
"drop-down."
msgstr ""
"要查看此聯絡人表單，請按一下\\ :guilabel:`合作夥伴`\\ 下拉選單右側的\\ "
":icon:`oi-arrow-right`\\ :guilabel:`（右）`\\ 箭頭。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:83
msgid ""
"Otherwise, if the fields do not auto-populate, manually enter the contact's "
"details."
msgstr "否則，如果欄位未自動填入，請手動輸入聯絡人的詳細資料。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:85
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Event` field is already populated. However, it is possible to "
"change the sponsor's event by selecting the relevant option under the drop-"
"down."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`活動`\\ 欄位已經填入。但是，可以透過在下拉式選單中選擇相關選項來變"
"更贊助商的活動。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:91
msgid "Sponsorship details"
msgstr "贊助詳情"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:93
msgid ""
"After configuring the sponsor's contact information, select or create "
"a :guilabel:`Sponsorship Level` or tier. By default Odoo **Events** creates "
"three sponsorship levels: *Gold*, *Silver*, and *Bronze*. Each of these "
"options displays the sponsor's logo on the event webpage in gold, silver, "
"and bronze colors, respectively."
msgstr ""
"配置完贊助商的聯絡資訊後，選擇或建立\\ :guilabel:`贊助等級`\\ 或層級。預設情"
"況下，Odoo **活動**會建立三個贊助等級：*金級*、*銀級*和*銅級*。這些選項分別會"
"在活動網頁上以金色、銀色和銅色顯示贊助商的標誌。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:98
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Sponsor Type` field, select how the sponsor should be "
"featured during the event."
msgstr "在\\ :guilabel:`贊助商類型`\\ 欄位中，選擇贊助商在活動期間的展示方式。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:100
msgid "Odoo **Events** supports three sponsor types:"
msgstr "Odoo **活動**支援三種贊助商類型："

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Footer Logo Only`: Displays the sponsor's logo in the footer of "
"the event webpage. Selecting this option creates a :guilabel:`Display in "
"footer` toggle button on the form. The footer logo is displayed **only if** "
"this button is toggled."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`僅頁尾標誌`：在活動網頁的頁尾顯示贊助商標誌。選擇此選項會在表單上"
"建立一個\\ :guilabel:`在頁尾顯示`\\ 切換按鈕。頁尾標誌**僅在**切換此按鈕時顯"
"示。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:105
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Exhibitor`: Features the sponsor as an exhibitor on the event "
"webpage under the *Exhibitors list* menu item. Selecting this option creates "
"two :guilabel:`Opening Hours` fields for the user to specify the exhibitor's "
"available hours."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`參展商`：在活動網頁的*參展商清單*選單項目下將贊助商展示為參展商。"
"選擇此選項會建立兩個\\ :guilabel:`開放時間`\\ 欄位，供使用者指定參展商的可用"
"時間。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:108
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Online Exhibitor`: Features the sponsor as an online exhibitor on "
"the event webpage under the *Exhibitors list* menu item, similar to "
"the :guilabel:`Exhibitor` option. However, this option also displays a "
"*Connect* button when hovering over the sponsor's thumbnail. When clicked, "
"attendees can connect with the sponsor online through their contact details."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`線上參展商`：在活動網頁的*參展商清單*選單項目下將贊助商展示為線上"
"參展商，類似於\\ :guilabel:`參展商`\\ 選項。但此選項還會在滑鼠停留在贊助商縮"
"圖上時顯示*連線*按鈕。按一下後，參與者可以透過贊助商的聯絡詳情與其進行線上連"
"線。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:114
msgid ""
"Both the :guilabel:`Exhibitor` and the :guilabel:`Online Exhibitor` options "
"display the sponsor logo in the footer of the event webpage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`參展商`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`線上參展商`\\ 選項都會在活動網頁的頁尾顯"
"示贊助商標誌。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:117
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Exhibitor` or :guilabel:`Online Exhibitor` option is "
"selected, an additional :guilabel:`Description` tab appears at the bottom of "
"the sponsor form. Enter a description for the sponsor to be displayed on the "
"sponsor's webpage."
msgstr ""
"如果選擇了\\ :guilabel:`參展商`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`線上參展商`\\ 選項，贊助商"
"表單底部會出現一個額外的\\ :guilabel:`說明`\\ 分頁。輸入贊助商的說明，以便在"
"贊助商網頁上顯示。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:121
msgid ""
"Finally, if the :guilabel:`Show on ticket` option is selected, registration "
"tickets display the logos of published sponsors for the event."
msgstr ""
"最後，如果選擇了\\ :guilabel:`在票券上顯示`\\ 選項，註冊票券將顯示該活動已發"
"布贊助商的標誌。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:125
msgid "Publish an event sponsor"
msgstr "發布活動贊助商"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:127
msgid ""
"To feature the sponsor as an exhibitor, the sponsor **must** be published "
"first on the event webpage."
msgstr "若要將贊助商作為參展商展示，贊助商**必須**先在活動網頁上發布。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:130
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Footer Logo Only` sponsor type is selected, toggling "
"the :guilabel:`Display in footer` button publishes the sponsor and displays "
"the sponsor logo in the footer of the event's webpage."
msgstr ""
"如果選擇了\\ :guilabel:`僅頁尾標誌`\\ 贊助商類型，切換\\ :guilabel:`在頁尾顯"
"示`\\ 按鈕會發布贊助商，並在活動網頁的頁尾顯示贊助商標誌。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:None
msgid "Event sponsors logos in footer in Odoo Events."
msgstr "Odoo 活動中頁尾的活動贊助商標誌。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:137
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`Exhibitor` or :guilabel:`Online Exhibitor` options, click "
"on the :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Go to Website` on the form. Then, click "
"the :guilabel:`Unpublished` toggle button at the top-right to publish the "
"sponsor page."
msgstr ""
"對於\\ :guilabel:`參展商`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`線上參展商`\\ 選項，按一下表單上"
"的\\ :icon:`fa-globe`\\ :guilabel:`前往網站`。然後，按一下右上角的\\ "
":guilabel:`未發布`\\ 切換按鈕以發布贊助商頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:141
msgid ""
"To see the published list of sponsors on the website, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Website app --> Events`. Then, click on the relevant "
"event. In the event sub-menu, click :guilabel:`Exhibitors list` to see the "
"list of published sponsors."
msgstr ""
"要在網站上查看已發布的贊助商清單，請導覽至\\ :menuselection:`網站應用程"
"式 --> 活動`\\ 。然後按一下相關活動。在活動子選單中，按一下\\ :guilabel:`參展"
"商清單`\\ 即可查看已發布的贊助商清單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:None
msgid "Event exhibitors on the website in Odoo Events."
msgstr "Odoo 活動中網站上的活動參展商。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:149
msgid ""
"If the sub-menu is **not** showing up on the event webpage, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` in the top corner. Then, click into "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab of the sidebar."
msgstr ""
"如果子選單**未**顯示在活動網頁上，請按一下右上角的\\ :guilabel:`編輯`\\ 。然"
"後按一下側邊欄的\\ :guilabel:`自訂`\\ 分頁。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:152
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, click the :guilabel:`Sub-menu (Specific)` "
"toggle button and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`自訂`\\ 分頁中，按一下\\ :guilabel:`子選單（特定）`\\ 切換按"
"鈕，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`儲存`。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:155
msgid "The website then displays the event sub-menu with various options."
msgstr "網站隨後會顯示活動子選單及各種選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:158
msgid ":doc:`event_booths`"
msgstr ":doc:`event_booths`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/event_sponsors.rst:159
msgid ":doc:`../attendee_experience/event_tracks`"
msgstr ":doc:`../attendee_experience/event_tracks`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo **Events** provides users with the ability to create custom event "
"tickets and ticket tiers with various price points."
msgstr "Odoo **活動**為使用者提供建立自訂活動票券和不同價位票券層級的功能。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:8
msgid ""
"It also allows them to sell event tickets in different ways: via standard "
"sales orders, through point of sales, and online through an integrated "
"website."
msgstr ""
"它還允許使用者以不同方式銷售活動票券：透過標準銷售訂單、透過 POS，以及透過整"
"合網站在線上銷售。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:16
msgid ""
"In order to sell event tickets in Odoo, some settings must first be enabled."
msgstr "為了在 Odoo 中銷售活動門票，必須首先啟用一些設定。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:18
msgid ""
"First, navigate to :menuselection:`Events app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Registration` section, there are several "
"different settings:"
msgstr ""
"首先，前往\\ :menuselection:`活動應用程式 --> 配置 --> 設定`。在\\ "
":guilabel:`報名`\\ 區段中，有幾個不同的設定："

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:21
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tickets with Sale`: Allows users to sell event tickets with "
"standard sales orders in the **Sales** app."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`透過銷售銷售票券`：允許使用者在**銷售**應用程式中透過標準銷售訂單"
"銷售活動票券。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:23
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tickets with PoS`: Allows users to sell even tickets with point "
"of sales in the **Point of Sale** app."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`透過 POS 銷售票券`：允許使用者在 **POS** 應用程式中透過 POS 銷售活"
"動票券。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:25
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Online Ticketing`: Allows users to sell event tickets online "
"through their integrated Odoo website."
msgstr ":guilabel:`線上售票`：允許使用者透過整合的 Odoo 網站在線上銷售活動票券。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:28
msgid ""
"To activate a setting, tick the checkbox beside the desired feature's label, "
"and click :guilabel:`Save` at the upper-left to enable it."
msgstr ""
"若要啟用設定，請勾選所需功能標籤旁邊的勾選方格，然後按一下左上角的\\ "
":guilabel:`儲存`\\ 以啟用。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:None
msgid "View of the settings page for Odoo Events."
msgstr "Odoo 活動的設定頁面檢視。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:34
msgid ""
"With these settings enabled, any event with paid tickets sold (either "
"through a sales order or through the website) features a :icon:`fa-"
"dollar` :guilabel:`Sales` smart button at the top of the event form. "
"Clicking the :icon:`fa-dollar` :guilabel:`Sales` smart button reveals a "
"separate page, showcasing all the sales orders (standard and/or online) "
"related to tickets that have been sold for that specific event."
msgstr ""
"啟用這些設定後，任何已售出付費票券的活動（無論是透過銷售單或透過網站售出）都"
"會在活動表單頂部顯示\\ :icon:`fa-dollar`\\ :guilabel:`銷售`\\ 智慧按鈕。按一"
"下\\ :icon:`fa-dollar`\\ :guilabel:`銷售`\\ 智慧按鈕會顯示單獨頁面，展示與該"
"特定活動已售出票券相關的所有銷售單（標準及/或線上）。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:None
msgid "View of an event's form and the sales smart button in Odoo Events."
msgstr "Odoo 活動中活動表單和銷售智慧型按鈕的檢視。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:46
msgid "Sell event tickets with the Sales app"
msgstr "使用\\ :guilabel:`銷售`\\ 應用程式販售活動票券"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:48
msgid ""
"To sell event tickets with sales orders, start by navigating to "
"the :menuselection:`Sales` app. Then, click :guilabel:`New` to open a new "
"quotation form."
msgstr ""
"要使用銷售單販售活動票券，首先前往\\ :menuselection:`銷售`\\ 應用程式。接著，"
"按一下\\ :guilabel:`新建`\\ 來開啟新的報價表單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:51
msgid ""
"After filling out the top portion of the form with the appropriate customer "
"information, click :guilabel:`Add a product` in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` "
"tab. Then, in the :guilabel:`Product` column, select (or create) an event "
"registration product."
msgstr ""
"在表單頂部填入適當的客戶資訊後，在\\ :guilabel:`訂單行`\\ 分頁中按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`加入產品`。然後在\\ :guilabel:`產品`\\ 欄中選擇（或建立）活動報名"
"產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:55
msgid ""
"To add an event registration product to a sales order, "
"its :guilabel:`Product Type` field **must** be set to :guilabel:`Service` "
"and the :guilabel:`Create on Order` field **must** be set "
"to :guilabel:`Event Registration`. These fields are accessible in the "
"product form of the event registration product."
msgstr ""
"若要將活動報名產品加入銷售單，其\\ :guilabel:`產品類型`\\ 欄位**必須**設定"
"為\\ :guilabel:`服務`，且\\ :guilabel:`訂單時建立`\\ 欄位**必須**設定為\\ "
":guilabel:`活動報名`。這些欄位可在活動報名產品的產品表單中存取。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:None
msgid "View of an event registration product form in Odoo."
msgstr "Odoo 中活動報名產品表單的檢視。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:63
msgid ""
"Once an event registration product is selected, a :guilabel:`Select an "
"Event` pop-up window appears."
msgstr "選擇活動報名產品後，會出現\\ :guilabel:`選擇活動`\\ 彈出視窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:None
msgid ""
"Standard 'Select an Event' pop-up window that appears on an event ticket "
"sales order."
msgstr "出現在活動票券銷售單上的標準「選擇活動」彈出視窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:68
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Select an Event` pop-up window, select which event this "
"ticket purchase is related to in the :guilabel:`Event` field drop-down menu. "
"Then, in the :guilabel:`Ticket Type` drop-down menu, select which ticket "
"tier the customer wishes to purchase, if there are multiple tiers configured "
"for that event."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`選擇活動`\\ 彈出視窗中，在\\ :guilabel:`活動`\\ 欄位下拉式選"
"單中選擇此票券購買相關的活動。然後在\\ :guilabel:`票券類型`\\ 下拉式選單中，"
"選擇客戶希望購買的票券層級（如果該活動配置了多個層級）。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:73
msgid ""
"When all the desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Add`. "
"Doing so returns the user to the sales order, with the event registration "
"ticket product now present in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab. The user can "
"proceed to confirm and close the sale, per the usual process."
msgstr ""
"完成所有所需配置後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`加入`。這樣做會返回銷售單，活動報名票"
"券產品現在出現在\\ :guilabel:`訂單行`\\ 分頁中。使用者可以按照一般流程繼續確"
"認並結案。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:78
msgid ""
"To re-open the *Select an Event* pop-up window, click on the event "
"registration product name in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, then click on "
"the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon."
msgstr ""
"若要重新開啟*選擇活動*彈出視窗，請在\\ :guilabel:`訂單行`\\ 分頁中按一下活動"
"報名產品名稱，然後按一下\\ :icon:`fa-pencil`\\ :guilabel:`（鉛筆）`\\ 圖示。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:84
msgid "Sell event tickets through the Point of Sale app"
msgstr "透過 POS 應用程式銷售活動票券"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:86
msgid ""
"To sell event tickets through a point of sale, the event registration "
"products must be configured to appear in the **Point of Sale** app."
msgstr "若要透過銷售點銷售活動票券，必須配置活動報名產品以在 **POS** 應用程式中顯示。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:89
msgid ""
"First, navigate to the product form for the event registration product by "
"going to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> Products` and selecting "
"the desired product. Under the name of the product, select "
"the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` checkbox to enable the product to be visible "
"in a :abbr:`POS (point of sale)`."
msgstr ""
"首先，前往\\ :menuselection:`銷售應用程式 --> 產品 --> 產品`\\ 並選擇所需產品"
"，以導覽至活動報名產品的產品表單。在產品名稱下方，勾選\\ :guilabel:`POS`\\ 勾"
"選方格，以使產品能夠在\\ :abbr:`POS（銷售點）`\\ 中可見。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:94
msgid ""
"After selecting, a :guilabel:`Point of Sale` tab appears where the user can "
"optionally provide additional information about the event tickets in "
"a :abbr:`POS (point of sale)`, such as its category or whether it can be "
"self-ordered."
msgstr ""
"勾選後會出現\\ :guilabel:`POS`\\ 分頁，使用者可以選擇性地在\\ :abbr:`POS（銷"
"售點）`\\ 中提供有關活動票券的額外資訊，例如其類別或是否可以自助訂購。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of an event registration product form configured to allow POS sales."
msgstr "配置為允許 POS 銷售的活動報名產品表單檢視。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:101
msgid ""
"With the products configured, navigate to :menuselection:`Point of Sale` app "
"and open a :abbr:`POS (point of sale)` register. The :abbr:`POS (point of "
"sale)` displays any open events with the corresponding event registration "
"products, as well as the event registration products themselves."
msgstr ""
"配置產品後，導覽至\\ :menuselection:`POS`\\ 應用程式並開啟\\ :abbr:`POS（銷售"
"點）`\\ 收銀機。:abbr:`POS（銷售點）`\\ 會顯示任何進行中的活動及對應的活動報"
"名產品，以及活動報名產品本身。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:105
msgid ""
"To learn more about configuring and selling products in a :abbr:`POS (point "
"of sale)`, refer to the :doc:`Point of Sale <../../../sales/point_of_sale>` "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"要進一步瞭解如何在\\ :abbr:`POS（銷售點）`\\ 中配置和銷售產品，請參閱\\ "
":doc:`POS <../../../sales/point_of_sale>`\\ 使用說明。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:111
msgid "Sell event tickets through the Website app"
msgstr "透過\\ :guilabel:`網站`\\ 應用程式販售活動票券"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:113
msgid ""
"When a visitor arrives on the registration page of the event website, they "
"can click the :guilabel:`Register` button to purchase a ticket to the event."
msgstr ""
"當訪客到達活動網站的報名頁面時，他們可以按一下\\ :guilabel:`報名`\\ 按鈕來購"
"買活動票券。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:117
msgid ""
"If the visitor is **not** already on the registration page of the event "
"website, clicking :guilabel:`Register` on the event website's submenu "
"redirects them to the proper registration page. From there, they can click "
"the :guilabel:`Register` button to begin the ticket purchasing process."
msgstr ""
"如果訪客**不**在活動網站的報名頁面上，按一下活動網站子選單上的\\ "
":guilabel:`報名`\\ 會將他們重新導向到正確的報名頁面。從那裡，他們可以按一下\\"
" :guilabel:`報名`\\ 按鈕來開始購票流程。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:122
msgid ""
"If different ticket tiers are configured for the event, the visitor is "
"presented with a :guilabel:`Tickets` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"如果為活動配置了不同的票券等級，訪客會看到一個\\ :guilabel:`票券`\\ 快顯視窗"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:None
msgid ""
"The tickets pop-up window that appears on the event's website when "
"'Register' is clicked."
msgstr "在活動網站上按一下「註冊」時顯示的票券快顯視窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:128
msgid ""
"From here, visitors select which ticket tier they would like to purchase, "
"along with a quantity, using the drop-down menu available to the right of "
"their desired ticket. Once the desired selections have been entered, the "
"visitor then clicks the :guilabel:`Register` button."
msgstr ""
"從這裡，訪客使用所需票券右側的下拉式選單選擇他們想要購買的票券層級以及數量。"
"輸入所需選擇後，訪客接著按一下\\ :guilabel:`報名`\\ 按鈕。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:132
msgid ""
"Then, an :guilabel:`Attendees` pop-up window appears, containing all the "
"questions that have been configured in the :guilabel:`Questions` tab of the "
"event form for this particular event."
msgstr ""
"然後會出現\\ :guilabel:`參加者`\\ 彈出視窗，其中包含針對此特定活動在活動表單"
"的\\ :guilabel:`問題`\\ 分頁中配置的所有問題。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:None
msgid ""
"The attendees pop-up window that appears on the event's website when 'Ok' is "
"clicked."
msgstr "在活動網站上按一下「確定」時顯示的參加者快顯視窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:138
msgid ""
"If multiple tickets are being purchased at once, there are numbered sections "
"for each individual ticket registrant, each containing the same questions. "
"However, if any question has been configured with the :guilabel:`Ask once "
"per order` setting, that question is only asked once, **not** for every "
"attendee making the reservation in the order."
msgstr ""
"如果一次購買多張票券，每個單獨票券報名者都有編號區段，每個區段包含相同的問題"
"。但是，如果任何問題配置了\\ :guilabel:`每筆訂單詢問一次`\\ 設定，該問題只會"
"詢問一次，**而不是**針對訂單中進行預訂的每位參加者詢問。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:143
msgid ""
"With all necessary information entered, the visitor can then click "
"the :guilabel:`Go to Payment` button. Doing so first takes the visitor to "
"a :guilabel:`Billing` confirmation page, followed by a :guilabel:`Payment` "
"confirmation page, where they can utilize any configured payment method set "
"up in the database to complete the order."
msgstr ""
"輸入所有必要資訊後，訪客可以按一下\\ :guilabel:`前往付款`\\ 按鈕。這樣做會先"
"將訪客帶到\\ :guilabel:`帳單`\\ 確認頁面，然後是\\ :guilabel:`付款`\\ 確認頁"
"面，在該頁面中，他們可以使用資料庫中設定的任何已配置付款方式來完成訂單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/promote_monetize/sell_tickets.rst:148
msgid ""
"Then, once the purchase is complete on the front-end of the website, the "
"subsequent sales order is instantly accessible in the back-end of the "
"database."
msgstr "然後，一旦在網站前端完成採購，隨後的銷售單即可在資料庫後端立即存取。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Registration Desk* feature in Odoo **Events** allows users to grant "
"access to registered event attendees as they arrive and store attendee-"
"related data in the reporting metrics."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **活動**應用程式中的*報到櫃檯*功能，讓使用者能在已登記的活動參加者抵達時"
"授予存取權限，並將參加者相關資料儲存於報表指標中。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:9
msgid "Registration Desk page"
msgstr "報到櫃台頁面"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:11
msgid ""
"On a mobile device (on the Odoo app or in a browser), navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Events app --> Registration Desk` to open "
"the :guilabel:`Registration Desk` page."
msgstr ""
"在行動裝置上（Odoo 應用程式或瀏覽器），前往\\ :menuselection:`活動應用程"
"式 --> 報到櫃檯`\\ 以開啟\\ :guilabel:`報到櫃檯`\\ 頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:None
msgid "The Registration Desk page in the Odoo Events application."
msgstr "Odoo 活動應用程式中的報到櫃台頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:17
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Registration Desk` box, the user has the option to "
"either :guilabel:`Scan a badge` or :guilabel:`Select Attendee`."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`報到櫃檯`\\ 方塊中，使用者可以選擇\\ :guilabel:`掃描徽章`\\ "
"或\\ :guilabel:`選擇參加者`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:21
msgid "Scan a badge"
msgstr "掃瞄證件"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:23
msgid ""
"To scan the code on event attendees' badges, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Events app --> Registration Desk` and tap "
"the :guilabel:`Scan or Tap` option."
msgstr ""
"若要掃描活動參加者徽章上的條碼，請前往\\ :menuselection:`活動應用程式 --> 報"
"到櫃檯`\\ 並點按\\ :guilabel:`掃描或點按`\\ 選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:27
msgid ""
"Odoo **must** be granted access to the camera being used for "
"the :guilabel:`Scan a badge` option to work."
msgstr ""
"Odoo\\ **必須**\\ 獲得對所使用相機的存取權限，:guilabel:`掃描徽章`\\ 選項才能"
"正常運作。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:30
msgid ""
"Once Odoo has access to the camera, a :guilabel:`Barcode Scanner` pop-up "
"window appears, showing a viewfinder box in the camera frame. The size of "
"the box can be manually adjusted by dragging the :icon:`fa-"
"crop` :guilabel:`(crop)` icon."
msgstr ""
"當 Odoo 取得相機存取權限後，會出現\\ :guilabel:`條碼掃描器`\\ 彈出式視窗，在"
"相機畫面中顯示取景框方塊。可以拖曳\\ :icon:`fa-crop`\\ :guilabel:`（裁切）`\\"
" 圖示來手動調整方塊大小。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Barcode Scanner window of the Registration Desk in the Odoo Events "
"application."
msgstr "Odoo 活動應用程式中報到櫃台的條碼掃描器視窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:37
msgid ""
"When the badge code is in the middle of the view-finder box, the code is "
"scanned and the :guilabel:`Barcode Scanner` pop-up window disappears. The "
"attendee is then granted access to the event and their attendance is logged "
"in the Odoo **Events** app."
msgstr ""
"當徽章條碼位於取景框方塊中央時，系統會掃描該條碼，:guilabel:`條碼掃描器`\\ 彈"
"出式視窗隨即消失。參加者即被授予活動存取權限，其出席記錄會記錄於 Odoo **活"
"動**應用程式中。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:41
msgid ""
"If the scanned barcode is invalid, an error pop-up message appears in the "
"upper-right corner."
msgstr "如果掃描的條碼無效，右上角會出現錯誤訊息彈出式視窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:44
msgid "Select Attendee"
msgstr "選擇參加者"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:46
msgid ""
"To manually grant access to event attendees, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Events app --> Registration Desk` and tap "
"the :guilabel:`Select Attendee` option."
msgstr ""
"若要手動授予活動參加者存取權限，請前往\\ :menuselection:`活動應用程式 --> 報"
"到櫃檯`\\ 並點按\\ :guilabel:`選擇參加者`\\ 選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:49
msgid ""
"This opens an :guilabel:`Attendees` page with all registered attendees "
"across events in the database. By default, this page opens in the :icon:`oi-"
"view-kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)` view, allowing the user to see an overview "
"of all attendees at a glance. Each attendee is displayed as a card with "
"their name, registered event, associated company (if applicable), ticket "
"type (if applicable), and registration status."
msgstr ""
"這會開啟\\ :guilabel:`參加者`\\ 頁面，顯示資料庫中所有活動的已登記參加者。預"
"設情況下，此頁面會以\\ :icon:`oi-view-kanban`\\ :guilabel:`（看板）`\\ 檢視開"
"啟，讓使用者能一目瞭然地查看所有參加者概覽。每位參加者會以卡片形式顯示其姓名"
"、登記的活動、關聯公司（如適用）、票種（如適用）及登記狀態。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:55
msgid ""
"Alternatively, users can view a detailed list of all attendees using "
"the :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(List)` view. Each attendee is displayed "
"on a line with their name, contact information, registered event, ticket "
"type, registration status, and an option to :guilabel:`Mark as Attending`."
msgstr ""
"或者，使用者可以使用\\ :icon:`oi-view-list`\\ :guilabel:`（清單）`\\ 檢視來查"
"看所有參加者的詳細清單。每位參加者會以資料行形式顯示其姓名、聯絡資訊、登記的"
"活動、票種、登記狀態，以及\\ :guilabel:`標記為已出席`\\ 選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Attendees page, via the Registration Desk, located in the Odoo Events "
"application."
msgstr "Odoo 活動應用程式中透過報到櫃台存取的參加者頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:62
msgid ""
"To grant access to an attendee and mark them as :guilabel:`Attended` in the "
"Kanban view, click on their card. The resulting pop-up window notifies the "
"user that the attendee has been marked as registered. "
"Click :guilabel:`Continue` at the bottom-left to mark the attendee "
"as :guilabel:`Attended`."
msgstr ""
"若要在看板檢視中授予參加者存取權限並將其標記為\\ :guilabel:`已出席`\\ ，請按"
"一下其卡片。產生的彈出式視窗會通知使用者該參加者已標記為已登記。按一下左下角"
"的\\ :guilabel:`繼續`\\ 可將參加者標記為\\ :guilabel:`已出席`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:67
msgid ""
"Alternatively, in the List view, click on the :guilabel:`Mark as Attending` "
"button on the attendee's line. The button then disappears and the attendee's "
"registration status changes to :guilabel:`Attended`."
msgstr ""
"或者，在清單檢視中，按一下參加者資料行上的\\ :guilabel:`標記為已出席`\\ 按鈕"
"。該按鈕隨即消失，參加者的登記狀態會變更為\\ :guilabel:`已出席`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:72
msgid ""
"Users can apply :doc:`filters and grouping options <../../essentials/"
"search>` on the :guilabel:`Attendees` page in both the Kanban and List views "
"to narrow down a large list of attendees or reorganize the page by specific "
"categories."
msgstr ""
"使用者可以在看板與清單檢視的\\ :guilabel:`參加者`\\ 頁面上套用\\ :doc:`篩選條"
"件和分組選項 <../../essentials/search>`\\ ，以縮小大量參加者清單範圍，或依特"
"定類別重新整理頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:76
msgid ""
"To do that, click the :icon:`fa-sort-desc` :guilabel:`(down arrow)` beside "
"the search bar to reveal a drop-down menu "
"with :guilabel:`Filters`, :guilabel:`Group By`, and :guilabel:`Favorites` "
"options."
msgstr ""
"若要執行此操作，請按一下搜尋列旁的\\ :icon:`fa-sort-desc`\\ :guilabel:`（向下"
"箭頭）`\\ ，以顯示包含\\ :guilabel:`篩選條件`\\ 、:guilabel:`分組依據`\\ 和\\"
" :guilabel:`我的最愛`\\ 選項的下拉式選單。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:81
msgid ":doc:`../../essentials/search`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../essentials/search`"

