"前往\\ :menuselection:`社交媒體推廣應用程式 --> 配置 --> 社交媒體`。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/social_marketing.rst:103
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Social Media` page there is a collection of all social "
"media options, each complete with a :guilabel:`Link account` "
"button: :guilabel:`Facebook`, :guilabel:`Instagram`, :guilabel:`LinkedIn`, :guilabel:`Twitter`, :guilabel:`YouTube`, "
